<h1>AutoResponder</h1>

<p>AutoResponder sends text messages to your callers, if you can't answer the phone. You can customize the message content. You can even set different messages for different occasions! (at work, with friends, etc.)</p>

<h2>History of changes</h2>

<h3>1.1.5</h3>
<ul>
	<li>Sent messages counter</li>
	<li>Small GUI improvements</li>
</ul>
